    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen, powered by the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 featuring eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including treated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain remains robust. The chassis maintains its composure through EDC (Electronic Damping Control) and a rigid subframe, offering exceptional lateral grip and precise turn-in. It is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car that balances track-ready kinematics with refined street usability.",
