    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seating is free of tears, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is exceptionally sound, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with full service records available for your review. It starts effortlessly, idles quietly, and the transmission delivers seamless shifts under all driving conditions. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it is ready for its next journey. This is a reliable, well-cared-for example that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
